We don't have an established apprenticeship program in the CoG. You could talk to Farrnusno or Destructress about helping out on the Dragon and Planes raids they run. If you're looking for older material on this sort of thing, do a search on the boards (usually under Events) for &quot;Mixer Hunts.&quot; There were a bunch of raids we ran in the first year of the CoG's existence, back before we did planes or dragon raids that involved getting as many folks as we could, and raiding dungeons as a method of training raiders in raid discipline. If I remember right, my first Mixer Hunt was my first time to lead a raid, so you can't get much more Trial By Fire than that. Somewhere on the CoG web site is a page that lists the Mixer Hunts, along with recaps of them. <br>
<br>
